snippet.title: Arcane Intro - Enemy (Extended No Rap) | Cinematic [w/ Download]
snippet.description:
This version of Enemy is a little different from the original, so i decided to make it a little longer right after i finished Arcane Act I, and share it with you guys at highest quality as possible, i hope you like it.
I would really really appreciate it if you click the like, share, or subscribe button. Enjoy Imagine Dragons - Enemy (Arcane Version)

Download here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vR0KuGGoRGB2MIvnuN9mFHTQ2LUWryeG/view?usp=sharing

1 hour mix: https://youtu.be/-Ppdcee68PI
With JID's part: https://youtu.be/SQdrTUqFHEM


Arcane: League of Legends

The delicate balance between the rich city of Piltover and the seedy underbelly of Zaun. Tensions between these city-states boil over with the creation of hextech a way for any person to control magical energy in Piltover, and in Zaun, a new drug called shimmer transforms humans into monsters. The rivalry between the cities splits families and friends as Arcane brings life to the relationships that shape some of League of Legends' famous champions including Vi, Jinx, Caitlyn, Jayce and Viktor.


#Arcane #League_of_Legends #Imagine_Dragons
